<br>
No but seriously after you do all the hand ins from Ixiblat and that Overking guy you will have a pearl.<br>
<br>
1. You hand this pearl to Zordak Ragefire (human) in Sol B who is a non-KOS merchant who spawns every 24 hours or so. He will give you a different pearl or something.<br>
<br>
2. Go to Skyfire and kill a KOS human Zordak Ragefire to spawn the dragon Zordakilicus Ragefire and kill him too. Loot his heart which is a container.<br>
<br>
3. Combine the pearl from Sol B in the heart to get a new heart which isn't a container.<br>
<br>
4. Do all the final hand ins as per the previous guide to get Ol' Droopy.<br>
<br>
